title: Did the Mayor of New York Bell de Blasieu once support the Sandinista Government? In Nicaragua?
subtitle: In May 2019, social media websites targeted the presidential democratic candidate, who was expected to be in 2020 to fill his previous political positions, as well as his decision to change his name.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: The mayor of New York Bell de Blasieu was formerly named Warren Wilhelm Jr. and once supported by the socialist government of Sandinista in Nicaragua.
